---

<AdsLayout
  title="Pub Crawl Barcelona by KING — #1 Party Tour | From €14.99"
  description="Barcelona's best pub crawl. ⭐ 4.9/5 · 863+ reviews · 3 bars · Free gift · VIP club entry · Skip every queue. Everyday from €14.99. Book now."
  ctaText="Book Now — €14.99"
  ctaHref="#book"
>

  <!-- ══ 0. URGENCY TOPBAR ════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="topbar" role="banner">
    <div class="topbar__inner">
      <span>
        🔥 <strong>Tonight's tour</strong> — spots filling up ·
        <strong>From €14.99</strong> · Rain or Shine · Everyday
      </span>
      <a href="#book" class="topbar__cta">Reserve My Spot →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ 1. HERO ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero" id="hero" aria-label="Hero">
    <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="hero__overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container hero__content">

      <!-- Eyebrow: trust signal immediately visible -->
