          <p class="feat-card__desc">A real person who knows every shortcut, every bartender, and every hidden gem in the city. The night runs itself.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feat-card">
          <div class="feat-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🌍</div>
          <h3 class="feat-card__title">Meet People from 50+ Countries</h3>
          <p class="feat-card__desc">Solo travelers, Erasmus students, groups from around the world. By bar 2, you'll feel like you've known them for years.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ INLINE CTA 1 ════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="inline-cta">
    <div class="container inline-cta__inner">
      <div class="inline-cta__text">
